# ── Model checkpoints (excluded from repo — too large or not needed) ──────────
# All fine-tuned model directories (not needed for the editor).
LayoutLM/layoutlmv3-funsd-paddle/
LayoutLM/layoutlmv3-funsd-tesseract/
LayoutLM/layoutlmv3-funsd-doctr/
